btrplace.plan

Class DependencyBasedPlanApplier

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.plan.DefaultPlanApplier
      • btrplace.plan.DependencyBasedPlanApplier
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReconfigurationPlanApplier

    public class DependencyBasedPlanApplier
extends DefaultPlanApplier
    A plan applier that relies on the dependencies between the actions composing the plan. Only unblocked actions are executed. Once executed, the unblocked actions are executed.

    This process is repeated until all the actions are executed. This process is ensure to finish iff their is no cyclic dependencies.

    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
